01:32:13,710 --> 01:32:16,330
Lisa...

1127
01:32:16,470 --> 01:32:20,330
this is, in many ways, the saddest
letter I've ever had to write.

1128
01:32:21,800 --> 01:32:25,710
I appreciate your many efforts
and kindnesses...

1129
01:32:25,850 --> 01:32:28,140
