1130
01:32:28,270 --> 01:32:32,480
My number is 45472, and my job,
the key to my survival-

1131
01:32:32,610 --> 01:32:37,740
"My number is 45472, and my job,
the key to my survival...

1132
01:32:37,860 --> 01:32:41,450
