1145
01:33:59,730 --> 01:34:01,980
"Dear Rube...

1146
01:34:02,110 --> 01:34:04,570
I know you asked us not to write...

1147
01:34:04,700 --> 01:34:06,860
so I'm not writing...

1148
01:34:06,990 --> 01:34:09,690
